---
// Standalone landing page — NO navigation
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>IBC for Business Owners | IBC Academy</title>
  <meta name="description" content="How business owners use the Infinite Banking Concept to fund growth, control their capital, and build wealth on their terms.">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          fontFamily: { sans: ['Inter', 'system-ui', 'sans-serif'] },
          colors: { gold: { DEFAULT: '#B8860B', light: '#D4A84B', dark: '#8B6914' } }
        }
      }
    }
  </script>
  <style>body { font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; }</style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-50 to-white min-h-screen">

  <main class="max-w-xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 lg:py-12">

    <!-- Minimal branding -->
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
      <span class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800">IBC<span class="text-gold">Academy</span></span>
    </div>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="text-center mb-10">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-purple-50 border border-purple-200 mb-4">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
        </svg>
        <span class="text-purple-700 text-sm font-semibold">For Business Owners</span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight mb-3">
        Stop Asking Banks for <span class="text-gold">Your Own Money</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
        How business owners use the Infinite Banking Concept to fund growth, control their capital, and build wealth — without bank approval.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- The Problem -->
    <section class="mb-10">
      <div class="bg-red-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-red-100 mb-6">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-red-800 mb-3">The Problem Every Business Owner Knows:</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-red-700">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-red-400 mt-1">✗</span>
            <span>Banks approve loans on THEIR timeline, not yours</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-red-400 mt-1">✗</span>
            <span>Good opportunities disappear while you wait for approval</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-red-400 mt-1">✗</span>
            <span>Your cash sits earning 0.5% while you pay 8%+ on debt</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-red-400 mt-1">✗</span>
            <span>Every financing decision costs you twice — interest out, opportunity lost</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-green-100">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-green-800 mb-3">What If You Could:</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-green-700">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-500 mt-1">✓</span>
            <span>Access capital in 24-48 hours — no application, no approval</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-500 mt-1">✓</span>
            <span>Pay yourself back the interest instead of a bank</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-500 mt-1">✓</span>
            <span>Keep your money growing even while you use it</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-500 mt-1">✓</span>
            <span>Build a capital reserve that compounds tax-free for decades</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Use Cases -->
    <section class="mb-10">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-4 text-center">Business Owners Use IBC For:</p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
        <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-100 text-center">
          <span class="text-2xl mb-2 block">🏗️</span>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">Equipment purchases</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-100 text-center">
          <span class="text-2xl mb-2 block">📦</span>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">Inventory financing</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-100 text-center">
          <span class="text-2xl mb-2 block">🏢</span>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">Real estate down payments</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-100 text-center">
          <span class="text-2xl mb-2 block">📈</span>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">Opportunity capital</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-slate-100 p-6 lg:p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 text-center mb-2">See How This Works</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500 text-center text-sm mb-6">Take the 2-minute assessment to see what's possible for your business.</p>

      <a href="/assessment"
        class="block w-full py-4 bg-gold hover:bg-gold-dark text-white font-bold text-lg rounded-xl transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-gold/25 text-center">
        Start Free Assessment →
      </a>

      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mt-6 text-sm text-slate-400">
        <span>Or:</span>
        <a href="/webinar" class="text-gold hover:underline">Watch the free workshop</a>
        <span>•</span>
        <a href="/discovery" class="text-gold hover:underline">Talk to Brad</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Brad -->
    <section class="text-center mb-8">
      <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center">
        <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-500">BR</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 mb-1">Brad Raschke</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-3">NNI Authorized IBC Practitioner</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 max-w-md mx-auto">
        I help business owners implement the Infinite Banking Concept — the wealth-building strategy that lets you become your own source of financing.
      </p>
    </section>

    <footer class="text-center text-xs text-slate-400 pt-6 border-t border-slate-100">
      <p>© 2026 IBC Academy</p>
    </footer>

  </main>

</body>
</html>
